.TH "HPC\-COMPOSE\-SETUP" "1" "" "hpc\-compose 0.1.53" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
hpc\-compose\-setup \- Create or update the project\-local settings file
.SH SYNOPSIS
.nf
hpc\-compose setup [OPTIONS]
.fi
.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
Create or update .hpc\-compose/settings.toml with profile defaults, environment files, explicit environment variables, and binary overrides.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB--profile\-name\fR \fIPROFILE\fR
Profile to create or update.
.TP
\fB--compose\-file\fR \fIFILE\fR
Compose file path recorded under the selected profile.
.TP
\fB--env\-file\fR \fIPATH\fR
Environment file path to append under profile.env_files.
.TP
\fB--env\fR \fIKEY=VALUE\fR
Environment variable entry written into profile.env.
.TP
\fB--binary\fR \fINAME=PATH\fR
Binary override such as srun=/opt/slurm/bin/srun.
.TP
\fB--cache\-dir\fR \fIPATH\fR
Cache directory default written under the selected profile.
.TP
\fB--login\-host\fR \fIHOST\fR
SSH login host used as the `up \-\-remote` destination (bare host, ~/.ssh/config alias, or user@host).
.TP
\fB--login\-user\fR \fIUSER\fR
SSH username applied to a bare login host for `up \-\-remote` (destination becomes user@host).
.TP
\fB--default\-profile\fR \fIPROFILE\fR
Set settings.default_profile to this profile name.
.TP
\fB--non\-interactive\fR
Do not prompt; use provided flags and existing settings as defaults.
.TP
\fB--format\fR \fIFORMAT\fR
Output format. Possible values: text, json.
.TP
\fB--color\fR \fIWHEN\fR
Controls colored output. Default: auto. Possible values: auto, always, never.
.TP
\fB--quiet\fR
Suppress progress indicators and non\-essential labels.
.TP
\fB--profile\fR \fINAME\fR
Profile name to load from .hpc\-compose/settings.toml.
.TP
\fB--settings\-file\fR \fIPATH\fR
Explicit settings file path; defaults to upward search for .hpc\-compose/settings.toml.
.TP
\fB-h\fR, \fB--help\fR
Print help (see a summary with '\-h').
.SH EXAMPLES
.nf
hpc\-compose setup
hpc\-compose setup \-\-profile\-name dev \-\-compose\-file compose.yaml \-\-default\-profile dev \-\-non\-interactive
hpc\-compose setup \-\-profile\-name dev \-\-cache\-dir '<shared\-cache\-dir>' \-\-default\-profile dev \-\-non\-interactive
hpc\-compose setup \-\-env 'CACHE_DIR=<shared\-cache\-dir>' \-\-binary srun=/opt/slurm/bin/srun \-\-non\-interactive
.fi
